THIS IS A BOMB?

00:22.272 --> 00:23.607
[ Russian accent ] IT'S A PHONE.

00:23.649 --> 00:24.942
NOW YOU HAVE TWO CHOICES --

00:24.984 --> 00:26.861
EITHER YOU DO

00:24.984 --> 00:26.861
WHAT WE'RE ASKING YOU TO DO,

00:26.902 --> 00:29.279
OR I HAVE TO PAY VISIT

00:26.902 --> 00:29.279
TO NATALIA AND LITTLE SASHA.

00:29.321 --> 00:32.616
EH? THEY GO TO SCHOOL

00:29.321 --> 00:32.616
SAME WAY EVERY MORNING.

00:32.658 --> 00:34.117
DID YOU KNOW THIS?

00:34.159 --> 00:35.786
IS NOT SAFE.

00:35.828 --> 00:37.997
ANYTHING.

00:38.038 --> 00:39.623
I'LL DO ANYTHING.

00:39.665 --> 00:42.918
OKAY. WHAT I'M ASKING

00:39.665 --> 00:42.918
FOR YOU TO DO IS...

00:42.960 --> 00:44.879
...ANSWER THIS PHONE.

00:44.920 --> 00:47.631
WHAT ARE YOU SUPPOSED TO DO

00:44.920 --> 00:47.631
WHEN THEY CALL YOU?

00:47.673 --> 00:49.008
I DO WHATEVER THEY ASK.

00:49.048 --> 00:52.427
THEN DESTROY THE PHONE

00:49.048 --> 00:52.427
AND TELL NO ONE,

00:52.469 --> 00:54.179
OR THEY'LL KILL MY CHILDREN.

00:55.389 --> 00:57.307
YOU, UH, INSTALL AND REPAIR

00:55.389 --> 00:57.307
TELEPHONE LINES FOR A LIVING?

00:57.349 --> 00:58.767
FOR 10 YEARS.

00:58.809 --> 01:02.646
I HAVE THREE

00:58.809 --> 01:02.646
MAJOR CONTRACTS RIGHT NOW.

01:02.688 --> 01:05.607
IF I'M ARRESTED,

01:02.688 --> 01:05.607
IT ALL GOES AWAY.

01:05.649 --> 01:08.485
AND YOU HAVE NO IDEA WHY

01:05.649 --> 01:08.485
THEY SPECIFICALLY TARGETED YOU?

01:08.527 --> 01:09.695
NO.

01:09.737 --> 01:12.406
I'M NOT PERFECT,

01:09.737 --> 01:12.406
BUT I TRY TO BE A GOOD MAN.

01:12.447 --> 01:13.824
MY PARENTS CAME TO BOSTON

01:13.866 --> 01:16.117
TO GET AWAY

01:13.866 --> 01:16.117
FROM THIS KIND OF THING --

01:16.159 --> 01:17.953
RUSSIANS HURTING RUSSIANS.

01:17.995 --> 01:20.121
AND IF YOU CONTACTED THE POLICE?

01:20.163 --> 01:21.707
THE RUSSIANS WILL KNOW.

01:21.749 --> 01:23.458
THEY SAY THEY'RE WATCHING.

01:23.500 --> 01:25.961
THIS BAR, I'VE BEEN HERE BEFORE.

01:26.003 --> 01:27.462
IT'S PROBABLY SAFE.

01:27.504 --> 01:28.714
AND YOU...

01:28.756 --> 01:29.798
YOU'RE NO COP.

01:29.840 --> 01:31.550
-NO. I'M NO COP.

01:29.840 --> 01:31.550
[ BEEPING ]

01:31.592 --> 01:32.676
CLONED.

01:32.718 --> 01:36.304
THIS PHONE RINGS,

01:32.718 --> 01:36.304
I WANT YOU TO ANSWER IT.

01:36.346 --> 01:37.556
WE'LL CONTACT YOU.

01:37.598 --> 01:39.140
THANK YOU, MR. FORD.

01:39.182 --> 01:41.894
WE'RE NOT GONNA LET ANYTHING BAD

01:39.182 --> 01:41.894
HAPPEN TO YOUR FAMILY.

01:41.936 --> 01:43.854
THANK YOU.

01:43.896 --> 01:46.147
OKAY, NOW,

01:43.896 --> 01:46.147
I PUT A TAP ON THE PHONE,

01:46.189 --> 01:48.525
SO IF THAT THING RINGS,

01:46.189 --> 01:48.525
WE'LL KNOW IT.

01:48.567 --> 01:50.318
ALL RIGHT, GOOD. WHAT ELSE?

01:50.360 --> 01:52.279
THERE'S ONE INCOMING CALL.

01:52.320 --> 01:54.155
THESE GUYS WERE THOROUGH.

01:54.197 --> 01:56.491
THEY WANTED TO MAKE SURE IF THEY

01:54.197 --> 01:56.491
CALLED, ANDREI WOULD ANSWER.

01:56.533 --> 01:58.702
YEAH, THEY, UH,

01:56.533 --> 01:58.702
THEY CALL IT ONCE TO TEST IT.

01:58.744 --> 01:59.787
EXACTLY.

01:59.828 --> 02:03.457
SO IF WE JUST

01:59.828 --> 02:03.457
CALL...THEM...BACK...

02:03.498 --> 02:05.333
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

02:05.375 --> 02:07.586
YOU GOING TO GET THAT?

02:07.628 --> 02:09.546
[ RINGING CONTINUES ]

02:16.053 --> 02:17.805
THIS IS PIETER.

02:17.846 --> 02:20.849
HELLO?

02:20.891 --> 02:22.643
MARCO.

02:22.684 --> 02:24.311
POLO.

02:34.279 --> 02:35.739
YOU SURE THIS IS THE PLACE?

02:35.781 --> 02:37.616
I'm sorry, am --

02:35.781 --> 02:37.616
am I -- am I sure?

02:37.658 --> 02:39.493
ELIOT, WHAT IS

02:37.658 --> 02:39.493
THAT RUSSIAN CARRYING?

02:39.534 --> 02:40.995
IT'S CALLED A SMARTPHONE, OKAY?

02:41.036 --> 02:43.163
SMARTPHONES READ E-MAILS,

02:41.036 --> 02:43.163
THEY HAVE GPS MAPS,

02:43.204 --> 02:44.999
THEY LINK TO AN ATOMIC CLOCK

02:45.040 --> 02:46.458
ON THIS LITTLE THING

02:45.040 --> 02:46.458
CALLED THE INTERNET.

02:46.500 --> 02:47.542
YOU EVER HEARD OF IT?

02:47.584 --> 02:48.710
COME ON, MAN.

02:48.752 --> 02:50.169
LOOK, A SMARTPHONE

02:48.752 --> 02:50.169
HAS AN OPERATING SYSTEM.

02:50.211 --> 02:53.132
IF IT HAS AN OPERATING SYSTEM,

02:50.211 --> 02:53.132
YOU KNOW I CAN HACK IT.

02:53.172 --> 02:55.092
[ BEEPING ]

02:57.427 --> 02:58.887
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:58.929 --> 03:00.055
OKAY.

03:00.097 --> 03:02.223
THINK I MAY HAVE JUST I.D.'d

03:00.097 --> 03:02.223
OUR BAD GUY.

03:02.265 --> 03:05.226
HIS NAME IS PIETER VOLOKH.

03:05.268 --> 03:08.022
HIM AND HIS CREW, THEY USED TO

03:05.268 --> 03:08.022
BELONG TO THE M-45s,

03:08.063 --> 03:10.398
EX-MILITARY HITTERS

03:08.063 --> 03:10.398
TURNED MAFIA BOYS.

03:10.440 --> 03:12.400
NOW, THEY TOOK A BIG HIT

03:10.440 --> 03:12.400
IN A BUST LAST MONTH.

03:12.442 --> 03:14.569
[ WHISTLES ]

03:14.611 --> 03:18.406
THEY LOST $20 MILLION

03:14.611 --> 03:18.406
IN MERCHANDISE TO THE POLICE.

03:18.448 --> 03:20.159
THAT'S GOTTA HURT.

03:20.199 --> 03:22.243
Okay, so -- so now look.

03:20.199 --> 03:22.243
We know what they're after.

03:22.285 --> 03:23.829
They're looking

03:22.285 --> 03:23.829
for a big-payout job

03:23.871 --> 03:25.413
SO THAT THEY CAN

03:23.871 --> 03:25.413
GET BACK ON THEIR FEET.

03:25.455 --> 03:27.124
NOW, I'VE I.D.'d THE PERP,

03:27.166 --> 03:29.751
I KNOW WHAT THEY WANT,

03:27.166 --> 03:29.751
AND I KNOW WHY.

03:29.793 --> 03:32.004
WHAT DID  YOU  DO

03:29.793 --> 03:32.004
WITH YOUR AFTERNOON?

03:32.046 --> 03:34.965
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT I'M  GONNA  DO

03:32.046 --> 03:34.965
WHEN I GET BACK THERE.

03:37.176 --> 03:39.469
[ MACHINE SHUFFLING ]

03:46.393 --> 03:49.188
[ SHUFFLING CONTINUES ]

03:52.482 --> 03:54.234
THINK HE'S INVOLVED?

03:54.275 --> 03:57.196
IT'S RUSSIAN MAFIA.

03:57.237 --> 04:00.032
THEY WEAR THEIR TATTOOS

03:57.237 --> 04:00.032
LIKE A RéSUMé.

04:00.074 --> 04:01.950
SEE THAT CATHEDRAL ON HIS NECK?

04:01.992 --> 04:05.495
THREE SPIRES,

04:01.992 --> 04:05.495
THREE TOURS IN PRISON.

04:05.537 --> 04:07.539
THE STARS ON HIS ARM

04:05.537 --> 04:07.539
MEANS HE'S A CAPTAIN.

04:07.581 --> 04:08.874
SO HE'S THE BOSS?

04:08.916 --> 04:10.792
I don't know. Probably.

04:10.834 --> 04:14.004
I RAN INTO SOME OF THESE CATS

04:10.834 --> 04:14.004
IN PETROZAVODSK.

04:14.046 --> 04:16.924
THEY BLACKMAIL INNOCENT PEOPLE

04:14.046 --> 04:16.924
LIKE ANDREI

04:16.965 --> 04:20.135
INTO COMMITTING CRIMES

04:16.965 --> 04:20.135
AND DROPPING OFF MONEY.

04:20.177 --> 04:22.554
THEN THOSE GUYS GET PICKED UP

04:20.177 --> 04:22.554
BY THE COPS

04:22.596 --> 04:23.638
OR THEY END UP DEAD.

04:23.680 --> 04:25.057
IT'S BRUTAL.

04:25.099 --> 04:27.267
WANT ME TO TASER HIM?

04:27.308 --> 04:29.436
No tasering, Parker.

04:27.308 --> 04:29.436
Not yet, anyway.

04:29.477 --> 04:30.562
Are they still in sight?

04:30.604 --> 04:31.855
I HATE THIS KIND OF CRIMINAL.

04:31.897 --> 04:34.108
WHAT EXACTLY WERE YOU DOING

04:31.897 --> 04:34.108
WHEN I CHASED YOU?

04:34.149 --> 04:36.359
I STOLE ART FROM RICH PEOPLE

04:34.149 --> 04:36.359
WHO COULD AFFORD IT.

04:36.401 --> 04:38.278
THESE GUYS?

04:36.401 --> 04:38.278
THEY TERRORIZE THEIR VICTIMS,

04:38.319 --> 04:40.655
THEY HARM FAMILIES,

04:38.319 --> 04:40.655
AND THE WORST PART?

04:40.697 --> 04:42.365
THEY MAKE INNOCENT PEOPLE

04:40.697 --> 04:42.365
COMMIT CRIMES.

04:42.407 --> 04:43.408
OH,  THAT'S  THE WORST PART?

04:43.450 --> 04:44.826
[ SCOFFS ]

04:44.868 --> 04:46.703
YOU BLACKMAIL AN INNOCENT MAN

04:44.868 --> 04:46.703
INTO BREAKING THE LAW,

04:46.745 --> 04:48.455
THE REST OF HIS LIFE

04:46.745 --> 04:48.455
HE'S GONNA FEEL SHAME

04:48.496 --> 04:49.831
OVER HOW YOU MADE HIM HELPLESS,

04:49.873 --> 04:52.000
OR GUILT OVER

04:49.873 --> 04:52.000
WHAT YOU MADE HIM DO.

04:52.042 --> 04:55.129
WE CHOSE CRIME.

04:52.042 --> 04:55.129
ANDREI DIDN'T.

05:00.467 --> 05:02.010
HURRY UP!

05:02.052 --> 05:03.303
I HURRIED!

05:03.344 --> 05:04.387
THEN I HURRIED AGAIN!

05:04.429 --> 05:05.722
I CHECKED IT THREE TIMES.

05:04.429 --> 05:05.722
IT'S CLEAN.

05:05.764 --> 05:07.057
CHECK IT AGAIN.

05:08.767 --> 05:09.851
[ METAL CREAKS ]

05:09.893 --> 05:12.062
[ BEEPING ]

05:15.274 --> 05:17.985
HEY! WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

05:19.861 --> 05:21.446
SH...

05:19.861 --> 05:21.446
WELL...

05:21.488 --> 05:22.447
UH...

05:24.699 --> 05:26.201
ELIOT!

05:26.243 --> 05:27.911
-MNH! MNHHH!

05:26.243 --> 05:27.911
[ CROWBAR CLATTERS ]

05:34.918 --> 05:35.794
UHH!

05:37.462 --> 05:39.214
YOU DON'T THROW CROWBARS

05:37.462 --> 05:39.214
AT PEOPLE!

05:39.256 --> 05:40.299
SORRY!

05:40.339 --> 05:42.759
"YOU DON'T THROW CROWBARS

05:40.339 --> 05:42.759
AT PEOPLE!"

05:42.801 --> 05:44.552
COULD HAVE JUST TASERED HIM.

05:44.594 --> 05:46.888
PROMISE ME WE'RE GONNA

05:44.594 --> 05:46.888
TAKE THESE GUYS DOWN HARD.

05:46.930 --> 05:48.556
I PROMISE.

05:46.930 --> 05:48.556
WHERE ARE THEY GOING?

05:48.598 --> 05:50.767
I WANT THIS TO BE EXCITING

05:48.598 --> 05:50.767
AND DRAMATIC.

05:50.809 --> 05:52.311
WELL, IT'S ALREADY EXCITING.

05:50.809 --> 05:52.311
LOOK WHERE THEY STOPPED.

05:52.351 --> 05:54.729
THEY REVERSED THE PHONE TAP.

05:52.351 --> 05:54.729
WE'RE BLOWN.

05:54.771 --> 05:57.607
THEY'RE GONNA KILL HARDISON.

05:57.649 --> 05:59.901
THEY'RE GONNA KILL  WHO?

05:57.649 --> 05:59.901
NO, THEY AIN'T!

05:59.943 --> 06:02.821
I BET YOU THEY AIN'T!

05:59.943 --> 06:02.821
NATE, YOU BETTER STALL!

06:02.863 --> 06:04.156
YEAH, COME ON.

06:07.117 --> 06:08.743
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

06:14.333 --> 06:16.210
WHOA. WAIT -- WAIT A MINUTE.

06:16.251 --> 06:18.128
LOOK, MY ONLY WAY OUT

06:16.251 --> 06:18.128
IS THE FRONT DOOR.

06:18.170 --> 06:19.546
ARE THEY COMING THROUGH

06:18.170 --> 06:19.546
THE FRONT DOOR?

06:19.587 --> 06:20.547
I DON'T KNOW.

06:20.588 --> 06:21.923
What you mean you don't know?

06:21.965 --> 06:23.508
YOU BETTER SAY SOMETHING.

06:23.550 --> 06:25.177
I SWEAR ON MY MAMA, I WILL BLOW

06:23.550 --> 06:25.177
A HOLE THROUGH YOUR BEDROOM

06:25.219 --> 06:26.636
AND SPIDER-MAN

06:25.219 --> 06:26.636
OUT THE SIDE OF THIS BUILDING.

06:26.678 --> 06:27.888
TELL ME SOMETHING.

06:27.929 --> 06:29.514
WE'LL TELL YOU SOMETHING

06:27.929 --> 06:29.514
IN A SECOND, HARDISON.

06:29.556 --> 06:31.225
WE'RE COMING THROUGH

06:29.556 --> 06:31.225
THE BACK DOOR.

06:31.266 --> 06:32.684
SHH.

06:39.733 --> 06:41.484
WHAT?

06:41.526 --> 06:42.736
YOU'RE NOT GONNA LIKE THIS.

06:42.777 --> 06:44.279
WHAT?

06:48.325 --> 06:51.286
SOMEBODY'S BEEN EATING

06:48.325 --> 06:51.286
OUR PORRIDGE.

07:04.091 --> 07:06.218
YOU DON'T HAVE TO BE SO ROUGH

07:04.091 --> 07:06.218
WITH HIM. THIS GUY...

07:06.260 --> 07:07.886
Nate?

07:07.928 --> 07:10.722
HOLD ON, HARDISON.

07:07.928 --> 07:10.722
THEY'RE NOT HERE FOR YOU.

07:10.764 --> 07:13.474
YEAH. YEAH, YEAH, I KNEW IT.

07:13.516 --> 07:14.893
[ CHUCKLES ]

07:14.935 --> 07:16.770
NOBODY CAN REVERSE

07:14.935 --> 07:16.770
MY PHONE TAPS.

07:16.811 --> 07:18.105
COME ON, MAN.

07:18.146 --> 07:19.981
I DON'T SEE WHY

07:18.146 --> 07:19.981
Y'ALL WERE GETTING ALL EXCITED.

07:20.023 --> 07:22.692
ALL RIGHT, I'LL DO

07:20.023 --> 07:22.692
WHATEVER YOU SAY.

07:22.734 --> 07:25.153
I STILL HAVE THE PHONE!

07:25.195 --> 07:26.613
WHAT ELSE DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

07:26.654 --> 07:28.698
THE RED PHONE AGAIN.

07:28.740 --> 07:30.825
NATE, THIS GUY'S NOT OUR BOSS.

07:30.867 --> 07:32.911
HE'S ANOTHER BLACKMAIL VICTIM.

07:32.953 --> 07:34.162
Yes, I know.

07:34.204 --> 07:36.957
I'M ABOUT TO MEET THEIR BOSS.

07:36.998 --> 07:39.084
GO ON.

07:46.967 --> 07:48.969
HELLO, DAD.

08:01.522 --> 08:02.983
NATHAN.

08:06.111 --> 08:08.738
GIVE ME A MOMENT.

08:06.111 --> 08:08.738
I WANT A WORD WITH MY SON.

08:08.780 --> 08:10.157
GO ON.

08:15.787 --> 08:17.331
I GOT OUT A WHILE AGO.

08:17.372 --> 08:19.374
YEAH, I-I KNOW.

08:17.372 --> 08:19.374
I KNEW YOU WERE OUT.

08:19.416 --> 08:21.542
I DIDN'T SEE YOU

08:19.416 --> 08:21.542
AT THE PRISON GATES

08:21.584 --> 08:22.836
WAITING TO PICK ME UP.

08:22.877 --> 08:25.464
YEAH, I WAS,

08:22.877 --> 08:25.464
UH, VISITING MOM'S GRAVE.

08:27.507 --> 08:31.178
SO, UH, WHAT'S -- WHAT'S

08:27.507 --> 08:31.178
A WASHED-UP BOOKIE LIKE YOURSELF

08:31.219 --> 08:33.096
DOING WITH A RUSSIAN

08:31.219 --> 08:33.096
BLACKMAILING CREW?

08:33.138 --> 08:35.515
I WENT TO PRISON

08:33.138 --> 08:35.515
'CAUSE I TOOK THE FALL

08:35.556 --> 08:38.435
FOR THE THREE FAMILIES.

08:38.477 --> 08:41.729
I DID MY TIME FOR THEM

08:38.477 --> 08:41.729
LIKE A STAND-UP GUY.

08:41.771 --> 08:42.856
YOU HEARD WHAT HAPPENED.

08:42.897 --> 08:43.898
YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.

08:42.897 --> 08:43.898
IT WAS ON THE NEWS.

08:43.940 --> 08:45.025
YEAH, I HEARD WHAT HAPPENED.

08:45.066 --> 08:47.402
ARTIE VAN,

08:45.066 --> 08:47.402
HE TURNED STATE'S EVIDENCE.

08:47.444 --> 08:49.696
-TURNED STATE'S EVIDENCE...

08:47.444 --> 08:49.696
-BLAH, BLAH, BLAH, BLAH,

08:47.444 --> 08:49.696
BLAH, BLAH, BLAH.

08:49.737 --> 08:51.031
...GAVE UP HIS LEDGER.

08:51.072 --> 08:52.366
20 YEARS OF PAYOFFS --

08:52.407 --> 08:54.993
THE McTEAGUES, THE O'HARES,

08:52.407 --> 08:54.993
THE DONNELLYS --

08:55.035 --> 08:57.620
ALL THE BIG FAMILIES

08:55.035 --> 08:57.620
ARE GOING DOWN BY LAW.

08:57.662 --> 08:59.914
NOW, ONCE UPON A TIME,

08:59.956 --> 09:01.708
THEY WOULD TAKE CARE OF SOMEONE

09:01.749 --> 09:03.168
WHO'S GONE INSIDE FOR THEM.

09:03.210 --> 09:05.628
I WENT TO JAIL FOR NOTHING.

09:05.670 --> 09:07.547
I WANT TO GET MY PIECE.

09:08.840 --> 09:10.008
WITH THESE GUYS?

09:10.050 --> 09:12.760
THESE GUYS THAT --

09:10.050 --> 09:12.760
THAT THREATEN CHILDREN?

09:12.802 --> 09:14.054
WHAT?

09:14.095 --> 09:17.265
GEEZ, YOU ALWAYS THOUGHT

09:14.095 --> 09:17.265
YOU WERE SMARTER THAN ME,

09:17.307 --> 09:19.267
BRIGHTER,  BETTER  THAN ME.

09:19.309 --> 09:22.187
EVERYBODY IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD

09:19.309 --> 09:22.187
ALWAYS TREATED ME WITH RESPECT,

09:22.229 --> 09:25.023
-BUT MY OWN SON --

09:22.229 --> 09:25.023
-WHAT DID YOU DO TO RESPECT,

09:22.229 --> 09:25.023
EXACTLY?

09:25.065 --> 09:27.192
MY SON, MY ALTAR-BOY SON.

09:27.234 --> 09:30.404
WELL, HEY, LISTEN TO YOU.

09:30.445 --> 09:34.074
NEVER BROKE THE LAW,

09:30.445 --> 09:34.074
YOU NEVER BROKE A RULE.

09:34.115 --> 09:35.616
LOOK AT YOU NOW.

09:34.115 --> 09:35.616
YOU'RE A THIEF.

09:35.658 --> 09:36.868
YOU'VE DONE TIME.

09:36.910 --> 09:39.329
IF YOU KNOW WHERE I'VE BEEN,

09:39.371 --> 09:42.582
THEN YOU KNOW

09:39.371 --> 09:42.582
THAT THIS IS MY TOWN NOW.

09:42.623 --> 09:44.543
AND I DON'T WANT YOU

09:42.623 --> 09:44.543
RUNNING GAME IN IT.

09:44.584 --> 09:48.296
ALL YOUR LIFE YOU THOUGHT

09:44.584 --> 09:48.296
YOU WERE BETTER THAN ME.

09:48.338 --> 09:49.964
NOW YOU'RE TRYING TO  BE  ME?

09:50.006 --> 09:52.967
YOU CAN'T BE ME.

09:53.009 --> 09:55.011
YOU DON'T HAVE THE STONES

09:53.009 --> 09:55.011
FOR THAT.

09:55.053 --> 09:57.931
YOU'RE NOT TOUGH ENOUGH.

09:55.053 --> 09:57.931
YOU'RE NOT RUTHLESS ENOUGH.

09:57.972 --> 10:00.392
YOU DON'T HAVE WHAT IT TAKES.

10:02.102 --> 10:04.812
YOU REMEMBER THE FIRST TIME

10:02.102 --> 10:04.812
I BROUGHT YOU INTO MY OFFICE?

10:06.606 --> 10:08.858
QUEEN AND HER COURT.

10:08.900 --> 10:11.736
GOT THAT? WATCHING?

10:11.778 --> 10:13.696
KEEP YOUR EYE ON THIS.

10:13.738 --> 10:14.864
IT'S THE LADY.

10:14.906 --> 10:16.991
NOW, PAY ATTENTION.

10:17.033 --> 10:18.952
WHICH ONE?

10:21.079 --> 10:23.415
YOU STILL DON'T GET IT, DO YOU?

10:23.457 --> 10:25.500
YOU GOT TO

10:23.457 --> 10:25.500
THINK THIS THROUGH, KID.

10:25.542 --> 10:27.001
YOU'RE JUST NEVER GONNA GET IT.

10:28.378 --> 10:30.547
YOU WEREN'T GOOD ENOUGH

10:28.378 --> 10:30.547
TO KNOW WHAT I WAS DOING THEN

10:30.589 --> 10:32.840
AND YOU AIN'T GOOD ENOUGH

10:30.589 --> 10:32.840
TO KNOW WHAT I'M DOING NOW.

10:34.593 --> 10:36.636
